snippet.title: Space Battle Royale | Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Calling all space pilots! It’s time to dominate the galactic arena. Fight your way to the final showdown inside the mysterious Cube, unleashing havoc and leaving only the debris of the rival ships behind. Oh, did you find yourself left among the wreckage? Upgrade your attributes, modify your ship – and get back into the carnage!

Space Battle Royale launches on Steam Early Access on November 16, 2023.

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2366400/Space_Battle_Royale/
